    <h3>Classic Horizontal Stripes</h3>
    <p>The signature horizontal stripe pattern used in early Finder windows and dialogs. Use the <code>.aqua-background-striped</code> class or apply <code>--aqua-background-classic</code> directly.</p>

    <%- example(`
<div class="aqua-background-striped" style="padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">
  <p style="margin: 0;">This container uses the classic horizontal stripe pattern from Mac OS X 10.0-10.3.</p>
</div>
    `) %>

